            <span class="MItem DateCreated">
               Posted on 2018-12-20 11:27:35            </span>
                                                <span class="Voter"><a href="/entry/signin?Target=discussion%2F1621%2Fannoying-message-pops-up-on-my-tv" class="VoteUp SignInPopup"><i class="ArrowSprite SpriteUp" rel="nofollow"><i>Vote Up</i></i></a><span>5</span><a href="/entry/signin?Target=discussion%2F1621%2Fannoying-message-pops-up-on-my-tv" class="VoteDown SignInPopup"><i class="ArrowSprite SpriteDown" rel="nofollow"><i>Vote Down</i></i></a></span>                    </div>
